    "selector_info": "Select the index seizure type. Acute symptomatic seizures (ASyS) occur within 7 days of the acute brain insult; first and second remote symptomatic seizures (RSyS) occur later — the curve shows the modelled risk of a (further) unprovoked seizure for each group.",
